320
00:14:47,924 --> 00:14:49,865
Uno specializzando in ginecologia.

321
00:14:50,005 --> 00:14:50,885
Non è un barrista?

322
00:14:52,166 --> 00:14:55,447
Mi scusi, professore.

323
00:14:55,486 --> 00:14:56,467
